text: Sultan Muhammad V (; born 6 October 1969) has been the Sultan of Kelantan since September 2010. He was the 15th Yang di-Pertuan Agong of Malaysia from December 2016 to his abdication in January 2019. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Alumni of the University of Oxford Category:Recipients of the Order of the Legion of Honour Category:Living people Category:Yang di-Pertuan Agong Category:People from Kelantan
